We help people and businesses to sell their products wherever they are online: websites, blogs or Facebook. 

Using a single, centralized e-commerce platform they can save time and efforts, preserve their online identities and reach their potential customers where they actually are. 

The name comes from "E-commerce made easy as blogging". Create a Shop on Blomming and you can bring it on your blog or website with a simple copy & paste, or within you Facebook page in just a couple of clicks. Share your products on any Social, Pinterest included, and engage your customers wherever they are online. And now you can sell on mobile, too. 

This is our vision of "Social Commerce": Publish, Share and Sell. Everywhere.

"Cool Vendor in E-Commerce 2012" by Gartner, Inc., Apr. 2012; 
"Premio Nazionale per l'Innovazione", Presidenza del Consiglio, Italy, Jun. 2012;
"Top 25 Promising Startups", Southern Europe, Tech Tour, Dec. 2011;

Aplicativos, Websites, Sistemas, E-commerces, Games e SEO (Otimização Google);
Desde 2004 no mercado;
Mais de 700 projetos entregues.

